Document: ChainIK3D
Path: godot/classes/class_chainik3d.rst
Summary: Describes the ChainIK3D node, a SkeletonModifier3D for applying inverse kinematics to bone chains.
Inherits: IKModifier3D < SkeletonModifier3D < Node3D < Node < Object
Inherited By: IterateIK3D, SplineIK3D

ChainIK3D is a SkeletonModifier3D that applies inverse kinematics to bone chains with a variable number of bones.
