Document: SkeletonIK3D
Path: godot/classes/class_chainik3d.rst
Summary: Base class for SkeletonModifier3D that automatically generates a joint list from bones.

Note: All methods in this class take an index parameter. This parameter specifies which setting list entry to return if the IK has multiple entries (e.g. settings/<index>/root_bone_name).
